      <title>鲍威尔重申美联储需要对通胀更有信心才能降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/powell-reiterates-fed-needs-more-confidence-on-inflation-to-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔向立法者重申，在政策制定者确信他们已经赢得了对抗通胀的战斗之前，美联储并不急于降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/powell-reiterates-fed-needs-more-confidence-on-inflation-to-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亨特选择市场平静，而不是保守党要求更广泛的减税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/hunt-says-uk-growth-better-than-expected-in-boost-for-tories</link>
      <description><![CDATA[杰里米·亨特在四个月内第二次削减个人税，并暗示英国执政的保守党将在竞选中承诺进一步削减个人税，英国财政大臣推出了一份选举年预算，该预算也经过仔细调整，以避免惊吓投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/hunt-says-uk-growth-better-than-expected-in-boost-for-tories</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 12:56:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约央行重燃地区银行担忧，国债延续涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/treasuries-fall-ahead-of-powell-s-remarks-and-us-jobs-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国债市场周三上涨，收益率跌至数周以来的最低水平，纽约社区银行(New York Community Bancorp)股价的最新暴跌再次引发了人们对美国地区银行健康状况的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/treasuries-fall-ahead-of-powell-s-remarks-and-us-jobs-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 09:01:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
